replyContent:
Hi, sorry you've had problems with the app.

If you follow the instructions exactly and it still has no effect, then of course you can get a refund. You can get it either via google play, or by emailing your order id to the support email.

Your comment about there being no 'try before buy' is also not valid - there's a free version of the app.
